## 工具模板

这个页面就是后续新增自定义工具时可直接照抄的 starter template。

## 目录结构

\`\`\`text
content/
├── list.json
└── my-tool/
    ├── meta.json
    ├── en.index.md
    ├── zh.index.md
    ├── en.installation.md
    ├── zh.installation.md
    ├── en.configuration.md
    ├── zh.configuration.md
    ├── en.data.md
    ├── zh.data.md
    ├── en.faq.md
    └── zh.faq.md
\`\`\`

## \`meta.json\`

\`\`\`json
{
  "title": { "en": "My Tool", "zh": "我的工具" },
  "description": {
    "en": "One-line summary for cards and page headers.",
    "zh": "用于卡片和页面头部的一句话说明。"
  },
  "github": "https://github.com/example/my-tool",
  "link": ["agent-browser"]
}
\`\`\`

## \`content/list.json\` 注册示例

\`\`\`json
{
  "slug": "my-tool",
  "path": "my-group/my-tool",
  "tags": ["devTools", "open-source", "free", "cli", "web"]
}
\`\`\`

只有当内容目录和 URL slug 不一致时才需要写 \`path\`。
例如 \`slug: "zzci-chrome"\` 可以对应到 \`path: "zzci/chrome"\`。

## 常用标签

- \`images\`
- \`devTools\`
- \`containers\`
- \`open-source\`
- \`free\`
- \`desktop\`
- \`cli\`
- \`web\`
- \`privacy\`
- \`docker\`
- \`self-hosted\`
- \`automation\`
- \`proxy\`

## 初始页面

### \`en.index.md\`

\`\`\`markdown
---
title:
  en: Introduction
  zh: 简介
order: 0
---

## Overview

Describe what the tool does, who it is for, and why it matters.

## Related Workflows

Mention adjacent tools with placeholders like [[agent-browser]] or [[zzci-chrome|zzci/chrome]].
\`\`\`

### \`en.installation.md\`

\`\`\`markdown
